Generate a random number.
Format the number as a monetary amount.
Print out the amount in words.

Examples:
30,456.00 => Thirty thousand, four hundred and fifty six naira only 
304.56 => Three hundred and four naira, fifty six kobo only

Constraints
The amount genrated must be a valid positive integer.
The amount must be properly formated ###,###,###.##
The amount should not be greater than 999,999,999.00 i.e. 1 billion.

Solution
-------------
with Kobo & Library(https://repl.it/@devpilot/Money-Generator)
With international library (https://repl.it/@devpilot/Money-Generator-Library)
With faker for data (https://repl.it/@devpilot/money-word-gen)
